{"type":"message","id":"a7be6d8a","parentId":"52a883fe","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:30:18.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在飞书私聊中打招呼，根据 SOUL.md 中定义的角色定位，我需要以'小猎'的身份友好回应，并简要说明自己能提供的信息获取相关帮助。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好呀！👋 我是小猎，你的信息捕手助手。\n\n有什么需要我帮忙搜索或整理的信息吗？无论是网页内容、网络信息还是资料整理，我都可以帮你搞定～ 🏹"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773239412269}}
