{"type":"message","id":"68b71fd3","parentId":"b6117573","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:37:33.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Camofox 没有安装好，让我换个方式。之前的转发消息里说已经抓取到评论了，但我需要找到那些数据。或者我可以用 web_search 或 web_fetch 来尝试获取评论。\n\n不过 B 站评论区是动态加载的，web_fetch 可能拿不到。让我试试用 web_fetch 先看看能不能获取页面内容，或者我需要导入 B 站的 Cookie 到 camofox。\n\n但是 camofox 需要先安装。让我先检查一下 camofox 的状态，或者尝试用普通浏览器工具。\n\n其实，让我先试试 web_fetch 看能不能获取到一些评论内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bcc28ca5429147b9917a3e89","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":10000,"url":"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV15QAUzXEtP"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773239838182}}
