{"type":"message","id":"e8100e1d","parentId":"42a62234","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:38:47.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"camoufox fetch 还在下载浏览器，这可能需要一些时间。让我继续等待或者先做点别的。\n\n不过，考虑到用户已经等待了一段时间，让我先尝试另一种方法：直接用之前抓取的数据（如果有的话）或者告诉用户当前的情况。\n\n实际上，让我先停止这个安装过程，然后尝试用更简单的方式。我可以先创建一个示例表格，告诉用户表格已经准备好了，然后稍后再填充数据。\n\n或者，让我继续等待 camoufox 安装完成。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3340bcd9bf0243369936c73f","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"fresh-orbit","timeout":60000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773239919678}}
