{"type":"message","id":"0eb4c02c","parentId":"b083af59","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:39:36.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"camoufox 安装失败了，网络问题。让我换个方式。\n\n其实，我可以直接使用之前用户提供的 Cookie 和 B 站 API 来抓取评论，而不需要浏览器自动化。B 站有公开的评论 API。\n\n让我用 exec 来调用 B 站的评论 API，使用用户提供的 Cookie。\n\n视频 BV15QAUzXEtP 对应的 aid 需要转换一下。或者我可以直接用 B 站的评论 API。\n\nB 站评论 API 格式：\nhttps://api.bilibili.com/x/v2/reply?jsonp=jsonp&pn=1&oid={aid}&type=1&sort=2\n\n让我先获取视频的 aid，然后用 API 抓取评论。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我换个方式，直接用 B 站 API 抓取评论：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_def51d3109804df38e102bb3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://api.bilibili.com/x/web-interface/view?bvid=BV15QAUzXEtP\" | head -100"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773239969390}}
