{"type":"message","id":"4c92fc5c","parentId":"9e34eed5","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:47:54.827Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户已经授权了，让我继续批量写入更多评论数据。我需要从 B 站 API 获取更多评论，然后写入飞书表格。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**📊 进度更新！**\n\n哥哥，评论数据正在持续写入！\n\n**当前状态：**\n- ✅ 已写入：29 条评论\n- 📊 总计：722 条评论\n- 🔗 表格链接：https://xcnb9qtctplo.feishu.cn/base/Vgkfb8Qveak3zrs8VPbcNzk8nOf\n\n由于评论数量较多，我可以创建一个自动化脚本来批量抓取并写入所有评论。让我先创建一个脚本文件，然后执行它来一次性完成所有评论的抓取和写入：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d7c1e855491b4df1a1281768","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env node\n\nconst https = require('https');\n\nconst AID = '116141955481993';\nconst TOTAL_PAGES = 37; // 722 条评论 / 20 条每页\n\nfunction fetchPage(pn) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const url = `https://api.bilibili.com/x/v2/reply?jsonp=jsonp&pn=${pn}&oid=${AID}&type=1&sort=2&ps=20`;\n    https.get(url, (res) => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        try {\n          const json = JSON.parse(data);\n          resolve(json.data.replies || []);\n        } catch (e) {\n          reject(e);\n        }\n      });\n    }).on('error', reject);\n  });\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  console.log('开始抓取 B 站评论...');\n  const allComments = [];\n  \n  for (let i = 1; i <= TOTAL_PAGES; i++) {\n    console.log(`抓取第 ${i} 页...`);\n    const replies = await fetchPage(i);\n    for (const reply of replies) {\n      allComments.push({\n        评论者：reply.member.uname,\n        评论内容：reply.content.message,\n        点赞数：reply.like,\n        发布时间：reply.ctime * 1000\n      });\n    }\n  }\n  \n  console.log(`\\n共抓取 ${allComments.length} 条评论`);\n  console.log('\\n前 10 条预览:');\n  allComments.slice(0, 10).forEach((c, i) => {\n    console.log(`${i+1}. ${c.评论者}: ${c.评论内容.substring(0, 50)}... (${c.点赞数}赞)`);\n  });\n}\n\nmain().catch(console.error);\n","path":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter/bilibili_comments.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773240467654}}
