{"type":"message","id":"15557c21","parentId":"aa08687d","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:50:09.965Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问能不能抓取评论区的图片。B 站评论中的图片是通过 API 返回的，在 content.pictures 字段中。让我检查一下之前抓取的 API 数据中是否有图片信息。\n\n从之前的 API 返回中，我看到有评论包含图片：\n```json\n\"content\": {\n  \"message\": \"有没有大佬帮忙翻译翻译是因为啥 [笑哭]\",\n  \"pictures\": [{\n    \"img_src\": \"http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/e307257281cc97cb9a43ce67b209e23a603268895.jpg\",\n    \"img_width\": 1920,\n    \"img_height\": 1080,\n    \"img_size\": 1045.16\n  }]\n}\n```\n\n所以是可以抓取的！我需要：\n1. 在表格中添加一个\"图片\"字段（或者用现有的\"图片链接\"字段）\n2. 重新抓取评论数据，提取图片 URL\n3. 写入表格\n\n让我告诉用户可以抓取，并继续执行。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"可以的哥哥！🎉 B 站评论区的图片是可以抓取的！\n\n从 API 返回的数据中，我可以看到评论包含图片信息（`content.pictures` 字段）。让我：\n\n1. **更新表格字段** - 确保图片链接字段正确配置\n2. **重新抓取带图片的评论** - 提取图片 URL\n3. **写入表格**\n\n让我先抓取带图片的评论数据：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_135921b834e2421a943d6341","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://api.bilibili.com/x/v2/reply?jsonp=jsonp&pn=1&oid=116141955481993&type=1&sort=2&ps=20\" 2>&1 | grep -o '\"pictures\":\\[[^]]*\\]' | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773240600979}}
