:\n    - img\n  - button \"回复\" [ref=e91] [nth=10]\n  - text: UP主觉得很赞 共6条回复，\n  - button \"点击查看\" [ref=e92] [nth=6]\n  - link [ref=e93] [nth=20]:\n    - /url: //space.bilibili.com/20765864\n  - link \"回忆终究会忘记\" [ref=e94]:\n    - /url: //space.bilibili.com/20765864\n  - img\n  - paragraph: 兄弟们，跳d3d24的，我找到解决办法了，还原你的计算机配置，你不要超频你再试试，我有时候d3d,有时候没事，经过一晚上找原因，终于锁定，是超频，你的电压没给够所以报错，我3080 0.85给的1890频率，负载高的地方老报错，就是电压不够，我恢复成默认，好了，不报错了，你们去把显卡内存都回复默认再试试，还不行试试cpu也默认，进不去游戏，画面中间一个白框，里面有显卡型号的是你系统问题，做系统能好，我就是这么解决的2个问题。\n  - text: 21小时前\n  - button [ref=e95] [nth=16]:\n    - img\n  - button [ref=e96] [nth=17]:\n    - img\n  - button \"回复\" [ref=e97] [nth=11]\n  - link [ref=e98] [nth=21]:\n    - /url: //space.bilibili.com/158187699\n  - link \"YueR61F\" [ref=e99]:\n    - /url: //space.bilibili.com/158187699\n  - img\n  - paragraph: 我这个有大佬知道吗\n  - text: 2026-03-10 18:04\n  - button [ref=e100] [nth=18]:\n    - img\n  - button [ref=e101] [nth=19]:\n    - img\n  - button \"回复\" [ref=e102] [nth=12]\n  - link [ref=e103] [nth=22]:\n    - /url: //space.bilibili.com/4510780\n  - link \"七濑w胡桃\" [ref=e104]:\n    - /url: //space.bilibili.com/4510780\n  - img\n  - link \"CD. 002176\" [ref=e105]:\n    - /url: https://www.bilibili.com/h5/mall/digital-card/home?act_id=104848&from=reply&f_source=garb&-Abrowser=live&hybrid_set_header=2&navhide=1&anchor_task=1\n    - img\n    - text: CD. 002176\n  - paragraph: 求救，这是啥问题啊，一进游戏就黑屏，然后就弹这个窗\n  - img\n  - text: 2026-03-09 21:12\n  - button [ref=e106] [nth=20]:\n    - img\n  - button [ref=e107] [nth=21]:\n    - img\n  - button \"回复\" [ref=e108] [nth=13]\n  - text: 共2条回复，\n  - button \"点击查看\" [ref=e109] [nth=7]\n  - link [ref=e110] [nth=23]:\n    - /url: //space.bilibili.com/20343910\n  - link \"指间旋律sj\" [ref=e111]:\n    - /url: //space.bilibili.com/20343910\n  - img\n  - paragraph: 有没有人遇到这种的？？\n  - img\n  - text: 2026-03-08 02:56\n  - button [ref=e112] [nth=22]:\n    - img\n  - button [ref=e113] [nth=23]:\n    - img\n  - button \"回复\" [ref=e114] [nth=14]\n  - tex