{"type":"message","id":"963daa1b","parentId":"96bbbc32","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:25:08.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to store durable memories before a memory compaction. Let me write the key accomplishments from this session to the memory file.\n\nKey accomplishments to record:\n1. B 站评论抓取项目 - 成功抓取 30 条评论到飞书多维表格\n2. 图片下载脚本 bili_fix.py - 成功测试下载 B 站图片（带 Referer 头绕过防盗链）\n3. 飞书表格链接和进度\n4. 技术要点：B 站 API 限制、图片防盗链解决方案\n\nLet me append this to the memory file.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b3d5fd1d0c964920ab69b17a","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-03-11 - B 站评论抓取项目\n\n## 项目进度\n- **目标**：从 B 站视频评论区抓取 722 条评论到飞书多维表格\n- **视频**：https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV15QAUzXEtP（生化危机 9 崩溃报错教程）\n- **当前进度**：30/50 条评论已写入（第一阶段目标 50 条）\n\n## 技术突破\n### 1. 浏览器自动化抓取\n- 使用 browser 工具模拟真人滚动加载评论\n- 每滚动 600px 停顿 2 秒，避免被检测\n- 成功绕过 B 站 API 限制（公开 API 只返回 3 条）\n\n### 2. 图片防盗链突破\n- **问题**：B 站图片直接访问返回 403（缺少 Referer）\n- **解决方案**：创建 bili_fix.py 脚本\n  - 添加 `Referer: https://www.bilibili.com/` 头\n  - 自动补全 URL 协议（// → https://）\n  - 去除压缩后缀（@xxx.webp）\n- **测试结果**：成功下载 2 张测试图片（410KB + 44KB）\n\n## 飞书表格\n- **表格链接**：https://xcnb9qtctplo.feishu.cn/base/Vgkfb8Qveak3zrs8VPbcNzk8nOf\n- **字段**：评论者、评论内容、点赞数、发布时间、图片地址\n- **已写入**：30 条评论（约 10 条带图片标记）\n\n## 待办事项\n- [ ] 继续抓取剩余 20 条评论（31-50 条）\n- [ ] 调试飞书图片上传 API（当前返回 params error）\n- [ ] 或采用方案 A：图片 URL 直接填入表格\n\n## 脚本位置\n- `/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter/bili_fix.py`\n- 用法：`python3 bili_fix.py <图片 URL> <文件名>`\n\n---\n*最后更新：2026-03-11 23:24*\n","path":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter/memory/2026-03-11.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773242676183}}
