{"type":"message","id":"29128a3c","parentId":"d1c48c90","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:40:24.592Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求把抓取成功的 10 条评论和图片添加到表格。我之前已经下载了 5 张图片，现在需要：\n1. 先获取这 5 张图片对应的评论数据\n2. 或者继续抓取更多评论，找到带图片的 10 条\n3. 将评论和图片信息写入飞书表格\n\n由于图片是表情包和装饰图，不是评论自带的图片，我需要：\n1. 继续抓取评论文本（31-50 条）\n2. 标记哪些评论带图片\n3. 将图片 URL 填入表格\n\n让我先继续抓取第 31-40 条评论，然后更新表格。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的哥哥！现在把抓取的评论和图片添加到表格！🏹\n\n让我先获取带图片的评论数据，然后写入表格：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_51653d5d01b1492a9747452d","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"function() { \n  // 获取评论区所有评论\n  const comments = [];\n  const commentElements = document.querySelectorAll('.root-reply-container, .reply-item');\n  \n  for (let el of commentElements) {\n    const userEl = el.querySelector('.user-name, .root-reply-container .user-name');\n    const contentEl = el.querySelector('.root-reply-container .content, .reply-content');\n    const likeEl = el.querySelector('.like-count, .root-reply-container .like-count');\n    const imgEl = el.querySelector('img');\n    \n    if (userEl && contentEl) {\n      const comment = {\n        user: userEl.textContent.trim(),\n        content: contentEl.textContent.trim().substring(0, 100),\n        likes: likeEl ? parseInt(likeEl.textContent) || 0 : 0,\n        hasImage: imgEl ? true : false,\n        imageUrl: imgEl ? imgEl.src.split('@')[0] : ''\n      };\n      if (!comments.some(c => c.content === comment.content)) {\n        comments.push(comment);\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  \n  return comments.filter(c => c.hasImage).slice(0, 10);\n}","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"639EEB8DC2BC1CADE83487F4838F4178"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773243614330}}
