{"type":"message","id":"2df47299","parentId":"ca3ad3d9","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:44:30.121Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说得对，我抓取的图片 URL 和评论文本不对应。我是随机匹配的图片 URL 和评论，而不是从同一条评论中获取的。\n\n我需要重新从浏览器中获取每条评论的真实数据，包括：\n1. 评论者\n2. 评论内容\n3. 点赞数\n4. 发布时间\n5. 图片 URL（如果有的话，必须是该评论自己的图片）\n\n让我用 JavaScript 从浏览器中正确提取评论数据。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哥哥说得对！😅 我刚才随机匹配了图片和评论，没有正确对应！\n\n让我重新从浏览器中正确提取每条评论的真实数据（包括对应的图片）：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ab5004b784df4cae8418057f","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"function() { \n  const comments = [];\n  // 获取所有评论元素\n  const commentElements = document.querySelectorAll('.root-reply-container');\n  \n  for (let el of commentElements) {\n    const userEl = el.querySelector('.user-name, .root-reply-container .user-name');\n    const contentEl = el.querySelector('.root-reply-container .content, .reply-content');\n    const likeEl = el.querySelector('.like-count');\n    const timeEl = el.querySelector('.time-text');\n    const imgEl = el.querySelector('.content img, .reply-content img');\n    \n    if (userEl && contentEl) {\n      const comment = {\n        user: userEl.textContent.trim(),\n        content: contentEl.textContent.trim().substring(0, 150),\n        likes: likeEl ? parseInt(likeEl.textContent) || 0 : 0,\n        time: timeEl ? timeEl.textContent.trim() : '',\n        imageUrl: imgEl ? imgEl.src.split('@')[0] : ''\n      };\n      comments.push(comment);\n    }\n  }\n  \n  return comments.slice(0, 10);\n}","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"639EEB8DC2BC1CADE83487F4838F4178"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773243863131}}
