{"type":"message","id":"3546cb13","parentId":"0b066148","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:48:41.548Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从页面扫描结果看，B 站这个视频评论区没有用户评论截图，只有视频封面和头像，需要向哥哥确认实际情况并提供替代方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**🎯 重要发现！** \n\n从页面扫描结果看：\n- ✅ 有 `/bfs/archive/` 图片（视频封面、推荐视频）\n- ❌ **没有评论区用户截图**（`/bfs/new_dyn/` 或评论容器内的图片）\n\n**实际情况：**\n这个 B 站视频的评论区**可能根本没有用户上传图片**！看到的图片都是：\n1. 视频封面\n2. 用户头像（`/bfs/face/`）\n3. 表情包/充电图标（`/bfs/garb/item/`）\n4. 推荐视频封面（`/bfs/archive/`）\n\n**💡 验证方法：**\n\n让哥哥手动检查一下：\n1. 打开 https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV15QAUzXEtP\n2. 滚动到评论区\n3. 看看有没有用户发的**问题截图**\n\n如果评论区确实没有用户截图，那：\n- **方案 A**：只抓取评论文本（图片字段留空）\n- **方案 B**：换一个有用户截图的 B 站视频测试\n\n哥哥，你能确认一下这个视频的评论区真的有用户截图吗？🏹"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773244096649}}
{"type":"message","id":"c24960a0","parentId":"3546cb13","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:50:10.779Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-11 23:50:09 GMT+8] Feishu[hunter] DM | 用户154215 (ou_689483ec5a555fe3639e3af84e52d8c3) [msg:om_x100b542cbdda8ca4b3643d8b9e346c3]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b542cbdda8ca4b3643d8b9e346c3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_689483ec5a555fe3639e3af84e52d8c3\",\n  \"sender\": \"用户154215\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 23:50 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"用户154215 (ou_689483ec5a555fe3639e3af84e52d8c3)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_689483ec5a555fe3639e3af84e52d8c3\",\n  \"name\": \"用户154215\"\n}\n```\n\n这个视频评论区真的有用户随评论文字搭配的图片"}],"timestamp":1773244210748}}
{"type":"message","id":"c63f2925","parentId":"c24960a0","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:50:22.315Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"哥哥确认评论区有用户图片，但我抓取不到。可能的原因是：\n1. 需要登录才能看到完整评论图片\n2. 图片是懒加载的，需要点击\"展开\"或\"查看图片\"才能加载\n3. 图片在回复的回复（楼中楼）里面\n\n让我尝试：\n1. 先导入 B 站 Cookie（哥哥之前给过）\n2. 点击展开更多评论\n3. 检查楼中楼回复里的图片","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的哥哥！既然确实有用户图片，让我调整策略重新抓取。可能是：\n1. 需要登录才能看到\n2. 图片在楼中楼回复里\n3. 需要点击\"展开\"才能加载\n\n让我用你的 Cookie 登录后再抓取：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_df0c84c5f9124b4facd154a0","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"function() { \n  // 检查是否有登录状态\n  const cookies = document.cookie;\n  const isLoggedIn = cookies.includes('DedeUserID');\n  \n  // 查找评论区的图片（包括楼中楼）\n  const allComments = document.querySelectorAll('.root-reply-container, .sub-reply-item');\n  const commentsWithImages = [];\n  \n  for (let el of allComments) {\n    const userEl = el.querySelector('.user-name, .sub-user-name');\n    const contentEl = el.querySelector('.content, .sub-content');\n    const imgEl = el.querySelector('.content img, .sub-content img');\n    \n    if (userEl && contentEl) {\n      const text = contentEl.textContent.trim();\n      // 排除太短的文本（可能是表情包描述）\n      if (text.length > 10 && !text.includes('首页') && !text.includes('大会员')) {\n        let imgUrl = '';\n        if (imgEl) {\n          const src = imgEl.src;\n          // 排除表情包和头像\n          if (!src.includes('/face/') && !src.includes('/garb/') && !src.includes('/activity-plat/')) {\n            imgUrl = src.split('@')[0];\n          }\n        }\n        if (imgUrl) {\n          commentsWithImages.push({\n            user: userEl.textContent.trim(),\n            text: text.substring(0, 100),\n            img: imgUrl\n          });\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  \n  return { \n    loggedIn: isLoggedIn, \n    totalComments: allComments.length, \n    commentsWithImages: commentsWithImages.slice(0, 10) \n  };\n}","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"639EEB8DC2BC1CADE83487F4838F4178"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773244210766}}
